generated_entities.entity: " this paper proposes a novel method of building polarity-tagged corpus from html documents . the characteristics of this method is that it is fully automatic and can be applied to arbitrary html documents . the idea behind our method is to utilize certain layout structures and linguistic pattern . by using them, we can automatically extract such sentences that express opinion. in our experiment, the method could construct a corpus consisting of 126,610 sentences .
